<details>
<summary><h2>Задание 109</h2><br>Выведите название страны, где находится город «Salzburg»</summary>

```mysql
SELECT Countries.name AS country_name 
FROM Countries
JOIN Regions ON Regions.countryid=Countries.id
JOIN Cities ON Regions.id=Cities.regionid
WHERE Cities.name="Salzburg";
```


```mysql
SELECT Countries.name as country_name 
FROM Countries, Regions, Cities
WHERE Regions.countryid=Countries.id
AND Regions.id=Cities.regionid
AND Cities.name="Salzburg";
```


```mysql
SELECT name country_name 
FROM Countries
WHERE id IN (
SELECT countryid FROM Regions, Cities 
WHERE Regions.id=Cities.regionid
AND Cities.name="Salzburg");
```

</details>

<details>
<summary><h2>Задание 111</h2><br>Посчитайте население каждого региона. В качестве результата выведите название региона и его численность населения.</summary>

```mysql
SELECT Regions.name AS region_name, 
    SUM(population) AS total_population 
FROM Regions INNER JOIN Cities 
    ON Regions.id=Cities.regionid
GROUP BY region_name;
```


```mysql
SELECT DISTINCT Rg.name region_name, (
    SELECT SUM(population) FROM Cities Ct
    WHERE Rg.id=Ct.regionid) total_population
FROM Regions Rg;
```


```mysql
SELECT DISTINCT Regions.name region_name, 
    SUM(population) OVER(
    PARTITION BY Regions.name) total_population
FROM Regions JOIN Cities 
    ON Regions.id<=>Cities.regionid;
```

</details>

<details>
<summary><h2>Задание 114</h2><br>Напишите запрос, который выведет имена пилотов, которые в качестве второго пилота (second_pilot_id) в августе 2023 года летали в New York</summary>

```mysql
SELECT name FROM Pilots
JOIN Flights ON Pilots.pilot_id=Flights.second_pilot_id
WHERE YEAR(flight_date) = 2023 
AND MONTH(flight_date) = 8 
AND destination = "new york";
```


```mysql
SELECT name FROM Pilots
JOIN Flights ON Pilots.pilot_id=Flights.second_pilot_id
WHERE destination LIKE "new_york" 
AND LEFT(DATE(flight_date), 7) = "2023-08";
```


```mysql
SELECT name FROM Pilots, Flights
WHERE Pilots.pilot_id=Flights.second_pilot_id
AND BINARY destination = "New York" 
AND flight_date RLIKE "^2023-08";
```

</details>
